- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with text analysis and natural language processing for mental health prediction on social media.
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is also likely as the paper focuses on social media data and its analysis for mental health prediction.
- cs.SD (Sound) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with detecting mental health status through text analysis, which could potentially include audio data.
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is also possible as the paper deals with a societal issue (mental health) and how technology (deep learning) can be used to address it.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is less likely but still possible as the paper uses deep learning-based models for mental health prediction.
